# CI documentation

When changing workflows or CI-related scripts:

1. **Policy** — `docs/ai/ci-cd/ci-governance.md` (source of truth for branches, PR rules, required checks).
2. **Mechanical** — `docs/ai/ci-cd/ci-operational-rules.md` (regex, job display names, commands, thresholds as implemented in YAML).

If workflow behavior and governance differ, follow the conflict order defined in `ci-governance.md` unless the user overrides.

After renaming jobs (`name:`) or adding checks, update `ci-operational-rules.md` so branch protection and docs stay aligned.
